A `None` value can't be serialized as bytes so something is wrong here. And this is never supposed to be `None` since it's already initialized at construction time as you can see [here](https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/3800/files#diff-a6042df3a2b6bca66372154b6cceff89R1457).

